utives       privacy policy terms of use about us contact us  salarycom all rights reserved us salaries canadian salaries purchase a salary report salaries by category salaries by income salaries by industry popular salaries negotiation tips benefits calculator search job openings job openings by state job openings by category education by career education by level education by major cost of living calculator cubn devan d ard insider trades for commerce union bancshares inc bulletin investor alert new york markets open in market snapshot analyst ratings expand keep open close expand keep open close expand keep open close expand keep open close expand keep open close commerce union bancshares inc nasdaq cubn go set alerts find a broker join td ameritrade market index overview profile news charts financials historical quotes analyst estimates options sec filings insiders marketstatecountryus commerce union bancshares inc after hours  quotes are delayed by  min jul    pm cubn quoteszigmancomposite   change   volume volume  quotes are delayed by  min quoteszigmancomposite previous close     change   day low day high    week low  week high   insider activity individual devan d ard mr devan d ard jr mba is president  director at commerce union bancshares inc tennessee president chief executive officer  director at commerce union bank springfield tennessee chairman at adventure science center a member at rotary club of nashville and chairman at we are building lives foundation he is on the board of directors at commerce union bancshares inc tennessee commerce union bank springfield tennessee and middle tennessee council inc he received his undergraduate degree from vanderbilt university and an mba from the university of alabama transactions date shares transaction value     derivativenonderivative trans at  per share      award at  per share      derivativenonderivative trans at  per share      disposition at  per share      derivativenonderivative trans at  per share     